channel.title: Any possible way to remove objects already placed?
channel.description: Hi, so i am trying to remove this cart from edgeville, i have searched the object ID in the object files but can't seem to find it. this is the cart that i'm talking about: [IMG]http://img525.imageshack.us/img525/620/c370b2ddd5e1eea3ed5d52f.png[/img] but yeah so i tried just adding another object in the exact same coord but it just put it on top of it xD So any ideas? :|

item.title: Any possible way to remove objects already placed?
item.dc:creator: @Team_Rocket Team_Rocket
item.description:
@Team_Rocket wrote:

You need to remove the object according to all the coordinates it takes up. For instance, it if takes up the space of 4 squares, you’d need to delete all four squares to make the object delete.

EDIT: You don’t need the Object ID.
